        {
            "id": 6048887,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉台積電領軍提振多頭士氣 漲135點收22712點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國與越南達成關稅協議，加上美國參議院通過《大而美法案》，且 9 月前可望降息，台積電有望受惠，台積電 ADR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 創高，激勵台積電今 (3) 日走揚，並提振大盤多頭士氣，終場漲 135.23 點或 0.6%，以 22712.97 點作收，成交量 3743.62 億元。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6048887/l/df8da57f28f171cd7e0670be85dbc9f0.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">台積電領軍提振大盤多頭士氣，終場漲135點收22712點。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股今天大多走揚，由台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 領軍，終場漲 5 元，以 1090 元作收，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2545:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2545\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2545-TW</a>) 收平盤，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，不過廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 跌 0.71%。其中，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 受惠 AI 伺服器帶動，BBU 迎出貨高峰，今天漲勢凌厲，大漲逾半根停板。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，台積電傳出為專注在高成長市場，有意淡出氮化鎵 (GaN) 市場，力積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6770:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6770\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6770-TW</a>) 與納微半導體 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVTS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVTS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVTS-US</a>) 建立合作夥伴關係，將採用力積電 8 吋 0.18 微米製程生產氮化鎵 (GaN) 產品，激勵力積電今日爆量漲停，鎖死 17.65 元。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>受惠 AI 伺服器及 800G 交換器高效運算滲透率提升，帶動 ABF 載板需求，ABF 載板族群今天也成為盤面亮點，南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>) 強攻漲停鎖死 124 元，景碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>) 大漲逾半根停板，新興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>) 則漲逾 4%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>由於美國與越南達成貿易與關稅協議，越南銷往美國商品課徵 20% 關稅，轉運商品稅率為 40%，鋼鐵族群因具有越南設廠題材，今天也紛紛表態。海光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2038:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2038\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2038-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，新鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2032:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2032\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2032-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，中鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2014:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2014\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2014-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，世紀鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9958-TW</a>)、中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)、新光鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2031:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2031\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2031-TW</a>)、大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>) 及東和鋼鐵 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2006:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2006\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2006-TW</a>) 皆有 2% 的漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>紡織與製鞋概念股同樣因美國與越南達成貿易及關稅協議，今天也有所表態。紡織類股如儒鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1476:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1476\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1476-TW</a>)、力麗 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1444:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1444\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1444-TW</a>)、南紡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1440:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1440\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1440-TW</a>)、福懋(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1434:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1434\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1434-TW</a>) 皆漲逾 2%；製鞋廠部分，來億 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6890-TW</a>)、鈺齊 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9802-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，志強 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6768:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6768\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6768-TW</a>)漲逾 4%，豐泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9910:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9910\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9910-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6048887",
